Package org.modelio.archimate.metamodel.layers.technology.behavior

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TechnologyEvent
    TechnologyEvent vnull Technology functions and other technology behavior may be triggered or interrupted by a technology event.
    TechnologyFunction
    TechnologyFunction vnull A technology function describes the internal behavior of a node; for the user of a node that performs a technology function, this function is invisible.
    TechnologyInteraction
    TechnologyInteraction vnull A technology interaction describes the collective behavior that is performed by the nodes that participate in a technology collaboration.
    TechnologyInternalBehaviorElement
    TechnologyInternalBehaviorElement vnull Abstract metaclass that represents internal behavior elements in the technology layer.
    TechnologyProcess
    TechnologyProcess vnull A technology process describes internal behavior of a node; for the user of that node, this process is invisible.
    TechnologyService
    TechnologyService vnull A technology service exposes the functionality of a node to its environment.
